sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import { useLocation } from 'react-router-dom' import { Container, Row, Col, Card } from 'react-bootstrap' const UserInfo = () => { const location = useLocation() const user = location.state || {} return ( {user.username} ID: {user.id} Discriminator: {user.discriminator} Locale: {user.locale} {/* Дополнительная информация о пользователе */} ) } export default UserInfo
